testCase.name: CreateTenantService should be able create an tenant with a valid name
CreateTenantService should not be able create an tenant with a alredy existing one
UpdateTenantService should be able to update an existing tenant
UpdateTenantService should not update an non existing tenant
UpdateTenantService should not be able to update an tenant's name to an alredy existing one
ListTenantService should be able to list an tenant with a valid id
ListTenantService should not be able to list an tenant with a invalid id
